{
  "stem": "17308.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I wouldn't see the German Wehr in that area particularly in force.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They were not.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But they used to-- they used to come down occasionally, checking.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because it was a little locality what they were not very much interested in.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I was.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, but there's very little to say.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because when, at some stage, the whole town was, like, encircled, I managed to find some old Frenchman who-- and I stayed with him there.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he-- then he hid me there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In a house, yeah.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, it wasn't long, because these raids were only-- they were coming and going.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were not searching entirely.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were going to big towns that would have had maintenance and everything.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But in those little places, I suppose they didn't have the-- the manpower to do it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They just came through.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They sent a squad or some few vehicles they send, and then they left.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, this was a particular house where the French guy was.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, it was a house.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In fact, it was a double-level house, you know, in the hill there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not especially.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was in-- I was there in that area, but not especially.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Well, there are alarms more than once, but it worked out right.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Till the end of the war.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I would say from about-- from '41 till '45-- end of '41.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I didn't have to be in hiding always.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's only when the Germans came around.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I stayed-- I had a room there by a French guy there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There wasn't much to be done.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I used to help occasionally in there, do a little manual work, but not much.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, not for Jewish.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They might be inquisitive why I was there the whole time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But they didn't show it officially.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
